{"word":"λούω","slug":"λούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λούω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> lavo ‘bathe, wash’] ‘cleanse with water’, usually of the whole body <b>bathe, wash<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><a href='B:510 9:37'>Ac 9:37</a>; <a href='B:510 16:33'>16:33</a>;</b> in imagery <b><a href='B:730 1:5'>Rv 1:5</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>bathe/wash oneself <a href='B:500 13:10'>J 13:10</a>; <a href='B:680 2:22'>2 Pt 2:22</a>;</b> in imagery (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> baptismal) <b><a href='B:650 10:22'>Hb 10:22</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λουτρόν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Λύδδα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}